translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_6f014d95:

#   e "That explains the general evasiveness."
    e "Eso explica la evasiva general."

# game/episode017.rpy:337
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_a8bc780f:

#   zi "One of the Taagmar dignitaries here on the station has agreed to meet us tomorrow."
    zi "Uno de los dignatarios Taagmar aquí en la estación ha accedido a reunirse con nosotros mañana."

# game/episode017.rpy:338
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_7f54a1e7:

#   c "Just the two of you?"
    c "¿Sólo vosotros dos?"

# game/episode017.rpy:340
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_ba0ecf13:

#   j "No, we’ve made sure you were included."
    j "No, nos hemos asegurado de incluirte."

# game/episode017.rpy:341
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_259f92ab:

#   j "They’ve allowed us to vouch for you."
    j "Nos han permitido responder por ti."

# game/episode017.rpy:342
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_2edfd7ae:

#   c "Finally, some good news."
    c "Por fin, buenas noticias."

# game/episode017.rpy:343
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_5fe760a4:

#   c "Good job, both."
    c "Buen trabajo a los dos."

# game/episode017.rpy:345
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_88387169:

#   "As we had some time to kill until tomorrow, we all went our separate ways."
    "Como teníamos tiempo hasta mañana, nos fuimos cada uno por nuestro lado."

# game/episode017.rpy:346
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_41e3c6ad:

#   "Some of the crew went for a meal on the station, while others stayed on the ship to avoid the crowd."
    "Algunos miembros de la tripulación fueron a comer a la estación, mientras que otros se quedaron en el barco para evitar la multitud."

# game/episode017.rpy:357
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_fight_d91e2ab2:

#   "Ignoring my own words on not drawing attention, I lunged at the fucker."
    "Ignorando mis propias palabras sobre no llamar la atención, me abalancé sobre el cabrón."

# game/episode017.rpy:359
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_fight_733ac962:

#   "I lunged at him."
    "Me abalancé sobre él."

# game/episode017.rpy:360
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_fight_0b2ec1e7:

#   c "You’ll take that back right now."
    c "Retira lo dicho ahora mismo."

# game/episode017.rpy:361
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_fight_0ea33c34:

#   "My fist connected with his beaked face and the alien went down."
    "Mi puño conectó con su cara picuda y el alienígena cayó."

# game/episode017.rpy:364
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_fight_fd1ee5fd:

#   c "Those are my sister and dear friend you’re talking about, you miserable piece of trash!"
    c "¡Estás hablando de mi hermana y de mi querido amigo, miserable pedazo de basura!"

# game/episode017.rpy:366
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_fight_eede9272:

#   c "Those are my dear friends you’re talking about, you miserable piece of trash!"
    c "¡Estás hablando de mis queridos amigos, miserable pedazo de basura!"

# game/episode017.rpy:369
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_fight_03723e40:

#   c "That is my sister you’re talking about, you miserable piece of trash!"
    c "¡Estás hablando de mi hermana, miserable pedazo de basura!"

# game/episode017.rpy:371
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_fight_018c4357:

#   c "That is my friend you’re talking about, you miserable piece of trash!"
    c "¡Es de mi amigo de quien estás hablando, miserable pedazo de basura!"

# game/episode017.rpy:372
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_fight_66524833:

#   man "I’m sorry, I didn’t mean-"
    man "Lo siento, no quise..."

# game/episode017.rpy:373
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_fight_8ee660b3:

#   c "Didn’t mean what?"
    c "¿No quiso decir qué?"

# game/episode017.rpy:374
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_fight_7192a721:

#   c "Your meaning was pretty clear."
    c "Su significado era bastante claro."

# game/episode017.rpy:376
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_fight_30b41eb7:

#   "I continued to rain down punches on the guys face."
    "Seguí dándole puñetazos en la cara."

# game/episode017.rpy:377
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_fight_02c28991:

#   "Our altercation hadn’t attracted a large crowd, for which I was thankful."
    "Nuestro altercado no había atraído a una gran multitud, lo cual agradecí."

# game/episode017.rpy:378
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_fight_b5304995:

#   "Station security didn’t seem too interested in what happened either."
    "La seguridad de la estación tampoco parecía muy interesada en lo sucedido."

# game/episode017.rpy:379
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_fight_6e252ef7:

#   "When the alien’s cries turned into pitiful sobs, I withdrew."
    "Cuando los gritos del alienígena se convirtieron en sollozos lastimeros, me retiré."

# game/episode017.rpy:382
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_fight_0618c670:

#   "Both Lilly and Vess looked a little shocked at me, but they both took my arm when offered."
    "Tanto Lilly como Vess me miraron un poco sorprendidas, pero ambas me cogieron del brazo cuando se lo ofrecí."

# game/episode017.rpy:385
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_fight_99ffcb72:

#   "Lilly looked a little shocked at me, but she took my arm when offered."
    "Lilly me miró un poco sorprendida, pero me cogió del brazo cuando se lo ofrecí."

# game/episode017.rpy:387
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_fight_3efa839d:

#   "A satisfied smile tugged at the corners of my sister’s mouth as we continued towards the Bastard."
    "Una sonrisa de satisfacción se dibujó en las comisuras de los labios de mi hermana mientras seguíamos hacia el Bastardo."

# game/episode017.rpy:389
translate spanish ep017_docks_encounter_fight_b05812bb:

#   "A satisfied smile tugged at the corners of my friend’s mouth as we continued towards the Bastard."
    "Una sonrisa de satisfacción se dibujó en la comisura de los labios de mi amigo mientras seguíamos hacia el Bastardo."

# game/episode017.rpy:394
translate spanish ep017_jade_c4f44779:

#   "Jade sat outside the Bastard on a container, hunched over her tablet, completely lost in thought."
    "Jade estaba sentada fuera del Bastardo en un contenedor, encorvada sobre su tableta, completamente perdida en sus pensamientos."

# game/episode017.rpy:396
translate spanish ep017_jade_b57fa023:

#   "She only noticed me when I sat down next to her."
    "Sólo se fijó en mí cuando me senté a su lado."

# game/episode017.rpy:398
translate spanish ep017_jade_aec4a347:

#   j "Oh hey, [p_name]."
    j "Oh hey, [p_name]."

# game/episode017.rpy:399
translate spanish ep017_jade_bc0be212:

#   c "Hey, not the most quiet spot to do some reading."
    c "No es el lugar más tranquilo para leer."

# game/episode017.rpy:400
translate spanish ep017_jade_b4f1880a:

#   j "I like the hubbub, all the noise somehow keeps me focused."
    j "Me gusta el bullicio, todo el ruido de alguna manera me mantiene concentrado."

# game/episode017.rpy:401
translate spanish ep017_jade_6ba22d62:

#   c "What were you reading?"
    c "¿Qué estabas leyendo?"

# game/episode017.rpy:403
translate spanish ep017_jade_8d57a18b:

#   j "Just some stuff about the Twi'll."
    j "Sólo algunas cosas sobre los Twi'll."

# game/episode017.rpy:404
translate spanish ep017_jade_f52b66d7:

#   c "A history book?"
    c "¿Un libro de historia?"

# game/episode017.rpy:405
translate spanish ep017_jade_131c2ccf:

#   j "Something like that."
    j "Algo así."

# game/episode017.rpy:407
translate spanish ep017_jade_f8fa634b:

#   j "Running into that Twi'll on Douvis and the destruction of the Taagmar home world triggered something."
    j "Encontrarse con ese Twi'll en Douvis y la destrucción del mundo natal de Taagmar desencadenó algo."

# game/episode017.rpy:408
translate spanish ep017_jade_7f875d40:

#   j "The way the Sovereignty is behaving there is awfully similar to what they did on our home world."
    j "La forma en que la Soberanía se comporta allí es terriblemente similar a lo que hicieron en nuestro mundo natal."

# game/episode017.rpy:409
translate spanish ep017_jade_c4e342ec:

#   j "I've been reading up on Paclerara and then I went down the rabbit hole."
    j "He estado leyendo sobre Paclerara y luego me metí en la madriguera del conejo."

# game/episode017.rpy:410
translate spanish ep017_jade_8859eb01:

#   j "I'd just arrived at the history of tea ceremonies that were in fashion on Luclite four hundred years ago, when you interrupted."
    j "Acababa de llegar a la historia de las ceremonias del té que estaban de moda en Luclite hace cuatrocientos años, cuando interrumpiste."

# game/episode017.rpy:411
translate spanish ep017_jade_a02ccb16:

#   c "Oh, tea sounds important."
    c "Oh, el té suena importante."

# game/episode017.rpy:412
translate spanish ep017_jade_29290089:

#   c "I won't keep you any longer in that case."
    c "No te retendré más en ese caso."

# game/episode017.rpy:414
translate spanish ep017_jade_b92225e4:

#   j "Haha, no, stay."
    j "Jaja, no, quédate."

# game/episode017.rpy:415
translate spanish ep017_jade_7f72f7af:

#   j "I already know more about tea than I should."
    j "Ya sé más de té de lo que debería."

# game/episode017.rpy:417
translate spanish ep017_jade_82ffc501:

#   j "I do wish we could visit Paclerara at some point, visit my mother's grave."
    j "Ojalá pudiéramos visitar Paclerara en algún momento, visitar la tumba de mi madre."

# game/episode017.rpy:418
translate spanish ep017_jade_e43a8bd4:

#   c "We'll try as soon as we're able."
    c "Lo intentaremos en cuanto podamos."

# game/episode017.rpy:420
translate spanish ep017_jade_01fd7748:

#   j "I'd appreciate that."
    j "Te lo agradecería."

# game/episode017.rpy:422
translate spanish ep017_jade_d806ba03:

#   "Jade and I stared into the distance, ignoring the many passers-by."
    "Jade y yo nos quedamos mirando a lo lejos, ignorando a los numerosos transeúntes."

# game/episode017.rpy:423
translate spanish ep017_jade_8f1914f4:

#   "She was the first to break the silence."
    "Fue la primera en romper el silencio."

# game/episode017.rpy:425
translate spanish ep017_jade_53e1450d:

#   j "I sometimes think it's crazy how far we've managed to come."
    j "A veces pienso que es una locura lo lejos que hemos llegado."

# game/episode017.rpy:426
translate spanish ep017_jade_bf4bc3c6:

#   c "I guess you don't mean the distance we've traveled?"
    c "¿Supongo que no te refieres a la distancia que hemos recorrido?"

# game/episode017.rpy:428
translate spanish ep017_jade_cb5244dd:

#   j "No, I mean, we've started out with a stolen ship, escaped the Sovereignty, visited a great many planets and got out of many hairy situations."
    j "No, empezamos con una nave robada, escapamos del Soberano, visitamos muchos planetas y salimos de muchas situaciones peliagudas."

# game/episode017.rpy:429
translate spanish ep017_jade_4acaaeca:

#   c "Well, if you put it that way."
    c "Bueno, si lo pones así."

# game/episode017.rpy:430
translate spanish ep017_jade_d125a393:

#   c "Though I mostly want a quiet drink in a quiet place, and someone else saving the galaxy or whatever the hell we're doing."
    c "Aunque lo que más me apetece es tomarme una copa tranquilamente en un lugar tranquilo, y que otra persona salve la galaxia o lo que demonios sea que estemos haciendo."

# game/episode017.rpy:432
translate spanish ep017_jade_a2aec314:

#   j "Still, we've had quite the adventure so far."
    j "Aun así, hasta ahora hemos vivido toda una aventura."

# game/episode017.rpy:433
translate spanish ep017_jade_f4e24f94:

#   j "And I think I'm better off now."
    j "Y creo que ahora estoy mejor."

# game/episode017.rpy:434
translate spanish ep017_jade_2374e24d:

#   j "Being an attendant was all I ever knew and I didn't really realize the wrongness of it all."
    j "Ser auxiliar era lo único que conocía y no me daba cuenta de lo malo que era."

# game/episode017.rpy:436
translate spanish ep017_jade_2269aaea:

#   j "I just couldn't imagine being anything else, if you know what I mean."
    j "Simplemente no podía imaginar ser otra cosa, si sabes a lo que me refiero."

# game/episode017.rpy:437
translate spanish ep017_jade_3275e9ef:

#   c "I think so."
    c "Creo que sí."

# game/episode017.rpy:438
translate spanish ep017_jade_12f129bb:

#   c "It's a rotten thing the Sovereignty did to you."
    c "Es una putada lo que te ha hecho el Soberano."

# game/episode017.rpy:439
translate spanish ep017_jade_3356e9cd:

#   c "No, what I did to you."
    c "No, lo que te hice a ti."

# game/episode017.rpy:440
translate spanish ep017_jade_3ee040d7:

#   c "I mean, you were a birthday gift..."
    c "Quiero decir, fuiste un regalo de cumpleaños..."

# game/episode017.rpy:442
translate spanish ep017_jade_69dbd27e:

#   j "Yes, I remember being terrified when I was to meet you for the first time."
    j "Sí, recuerdo estar aterrorizada cuando iba a conocerte por primera vez."

# game/episode017.rpy:443
translate spanish ep017_jade_6752e3a3:

#   j "I was relieved you were such a nice guy, because I've heard some horror stories over the years."
    j "Me sentí aliviado de que fueras tan buen tipo, porque he oído algunas historias de horror a lo largo de los años."

# game/episode017.rpy:445
translate spanish ep017_jade_d5c4100d:

#   j "Girls getting beat up, used by the entire family for their pleasure, or made to suffer in some sex dungeon."
    j "Chicas golpeadas, utilizadas por toda la familia para su placer, o hechas sufrir en alguna mazmorra sexual."

# game/episode017.rpy:446
translate spanish ep017_jade_44985f6b:

#   j "All things considered, I didn't have it so bad."
    j "Considerando todo, no lo tenía tan mal."

# game/episode017.rpy:447
translate spanish ep017_jade_79c770a2:

#   c "Still, you were supposed to be my property."
    c "Aún así, se suponía que eras de mi propiedad."

# game/episode017.rpy:449
translate spanish ep017_jade_f467471f:

#   c "I could have refused, like Thim did."
    c "Podría haberme negado, como hizo Thim."

# game/episode017.rpy:451
translate spanish ep017_jade_c19c5a5d:

#   c "I could have refused."
    c "Podría haberme negado."

# game/episode017.rpy:453
translate spanish ep017_jade_22e29c09:

#   j "That would have been noble and I might have ended up with a creepy old man, chained to a post."
    j "Eso habría sido noble y podría haber acabado con un viejo espeluznante, encadenado a un poste."

# game/episode017.rpy:454
translate spanish ep017_jade_3e05188b:

#   j "I'm not saying you shouldn't feel bad about the treatment of Twi'll, or me personally, but for me everything worked out in the end."
    j "No digo que no debas sentirte mal por el trato a Twi'll, o a mí personalmente, pero para mí al final todo salió bien."

# game/episode017.rpy:456
translate spanish ep017_jade_239ea88f:

#   j "I got my freedom and got to stay with the man I came to love."
    j "Conseguí mi libertad y pude quedarme con el hombre al que llegué a amar."

# game/episode017.rpy:457
translate spanish ep017_jade_2f250e97:

#   j "So, all in all, I had a better deal."
    j "Así que, en general, he hecho un mejor negocio."

# game/episode017.rpy:458
translate spanish ep017_jade_8c1853f3:

#   c "I can't really imagine what you've been through."
    c "Realmente no puedo imaginar por lo que has pasado."

# game/episode017.rpy:459
translate spanish ep017_jade_fa562646:

#   c "I'm sorry I never thought to ask, but were you just dumped into my lap?"
    c "Siento no habértelo preguntado, pero ¿te han dejado en mi regazo?"

# game/episode017.rpy:461
translate spanish ep017_jade_39ea0227:

#   j "No, not at all."
    j "No, en absoluto."

# game/episode017.rpy:463
translate spanish ep017_jade_d69cf7f9:

#   j "The Sovereignty makes sure the attendants get all the training they need."
    j "El Soberano se asegura de que los asistentes reciban toda la formación que necesitan."

# game/episode017.rpy:464
translate spanish ep017_jade_9be70cbf:

#   j "In contrast to the dire treatment most Twi'll receive after becoming an attendant, the Sovereignty makes very sure their valuable assets are protected."
    j "En contraste con el pésimo trato que reciben la mayoría de los Twi tras convertirse en asistentes, el Soberano se asegura de que sus valiosos activos estén protegidos."

# game/episode017.rpy:465
translate spanish ep017_jade_bc6756f0:

#   j "So genders aren't allowed to mingle and any physical contact is forbidden, even between members of the same sex."
    j "Así pues, los sexos no pueden mezclarse y está prohibido cualquier contacto físico, incluso entre miembros del mismo sexo."

# game/episode017.rpy:466
translate spanish ep017_jade_bbdad92c:

#   j "Which was a challenge, considering the amount of detailed audiovisual instruction we received."
    j "Fue todo un reto, teniendo en cuenta la cantidad de instrucciones audiovisuales detalladas que recibimos."

# game/episode017.rpy:468
translate spanish ep017_jade_4e161613:

#   j "I don't have to tell you the effect of too much stimulating imagery on the minds of youngsters just finding out the things down below is for something more than peeing..."
    j "No hace falta que te cuente el efecto de demasiadas imágenes estimulantes en las mentes de los más jóvenes al descubrir que las cosas de abajo sirven para algo más que para mear..."

# game/episode017.rpy:469
translate spanish ep017_jade_9a60c2bb:

#   c "Nope."
    c "No."

# game/episode017.rpy:471
translate spanish ep017_jade_613e0719:

#   j "Then training was over and we were sent out."
    j "Luego terminó el entrenamiento y nos enviaron a la calle."

# game/episode017.rpy:473
translate spanish ep017_jade_a341cc0b:

#   j "And I found myself naked on a couch in a mansion, head full of knowledge to please a human and absolutely no clue what to do at all."
    j "Y me encontré desnuda en el sofá de una mansión, con la cabeza llena de conocimientos para complacer a un humano y sin la menor idea de qué hacer."

# game/episode017.rpy:474
translate spanish ep017_jade_47a65c08:

#   c "I remember that moment."
    c "Recuerdo ese momento."

# game/episode017.rpy:475
translate spanish ep017_jade_15af1c9b:

#   c "Everybody clapping as I walked into the room."
    c "Todo el mundo aplaudiendo cuando entré en la habitación."

# game/episode017.rpy:476
translate spanish ep017_jade_2006f9fd:

#   c "My father standing proudly in the center, slapping me on the shoulder."
    c "Mi padre de pie orgulloso en el centro, dándome una palmada en el hombro."

# game/episode017.rpy:477
translate spanish ep017_jade_35ccee82:

#   c "Him telling me I'd finally become a man, or some inane bullshit with a similar meaning."
    c "Que me dijera que por fin me había convertido en un hombre, o alguna tontería con un significado similar."

# game/episode017.rpy:478
translate spanish ep017_jade_751c0cab:

#   c "I'm so glad we left that all behind."
    c "Me alegro mucho de haber dejado todo eso atrás."

# game/episode017.rpy:480
translate spanish ep017_jade_cc5e28a7:

#   j "As am I."
    j "Como yo."

# game/episode017.rpy:481
translate spanish ep017_jade_a2fbbdac:

#   c "You've got to wonder though, why nobody has ever thought to burn the whole Sovereignty to the ground."
    c "Sin embargo, cabe preguntarse por qué a nadie se le ha ocurrido quemar toda la Soberanía hasta los cimientos."

# game/episode017.rpy:483
translate spanish ep017_jade_9a1cd484:

#   j "I'm sure it's been tried."
    j "Seguro que lo han intentado."

# game/episode017.rpy:485
translate spanish ep017_jade_516e4a65:

#   j "And I know that there have been attempts by the Twi'll, especially in the early days after we were conquered."
    j "Y sé que ha habido intentos por parte de los Twi'll, especialmente en los primeros días tras nuestra conquista."

# game/episode017.rpy:486
translate spanish ep017_jade_ab45f477:

#   j "The Sovereignty is quick to stamp those fires out..."
    j "La Soberanía se apresura a apagar esos fuegos..."

# game/episode017.rpy:488
translate spanish ep017_jade_b9f96482:

#   j "So it's rather hard to topple an empire like the Sovereignty with a few scattered rebels."
    j "Así que es bastante difícil derrocar un imperio como el Soberano con unos pocos rebeldes dispersos."

# game/episode017.rpy:489
translate spanish ep017_jade_70207868:

#   c "Yes, I’m sure it’s a challenge, but one can hope."
    c "Sí, seguro que es un reto, pero cabe esperar."

# game/episode017.rpy:491
translate spanish ep017_jade_a7627367:

#   j "True, true."
    j "Cierto, cierto."

# game/episode017.rpy:493
translate spanish ep017_jade_c8f96d6c:

#   "We continued watching the crowd flow among us in silence for a while."
    "Seguimos observando a la multitud que fluye entre nosotros en silencio durante un rato."

# game/episode017.rpy:494
translate spanish ep017_jade_92bce088:

#   c "Well, I’ll leave you to learn everything there is to know about tea."
    c "Bueno, te dejo para que aprendas todo lo que hay que saber sobre el té."

# game/episode017.rpy:496
translate spanish ep017_jade_0c7bf418:

#   j "I’ll tell you all about someone called Earl Grey, once I’m done."
    j "Te contaré todo sobre alguien llamado Earl Grey, cuando termine."

# game/episode017.rpy:498
translate spanish ep017_jade_c0e00c6b:

#   c "Can’t wait!"
    c "Estoy impaciente."

# game/episode017.rpy:510
translate spanish ep017_first_dream_1cd05b35:

#   woman "Come to us, [p_name]."
    woman "Ven a nosotros, [p_name]."

# game/episode017.rpy:517
translate spanish ep017_first_dream_37bf75b5:

#   woman "We require a Tasting!"
    woman "Exigimos una degustación"

# game/episode017.rpy:518
translate spanish ep017_first_dream_97cd46cb:

#   woman "You’re ours now!"
    woman "¡Ahora eres nuestro!"

# game/episode017.rpy:519
translate spanish ep017_first_dream_eae746a4:

#   woman "Don’t resist."
    woman "No te resistas."

# game/episode017.rpy:526
translate spanish ep017_first_dream_f7468510:

#   woman "We long to Taste the fornication."
    woman "Anhelamos Probar la fornicación."

# game/episode017.rpy:527
translate spanish ep017_first_dream_073ddb03:

#   woman "The debauchery, so sweet on our tongue."
    woman "El libertinaje, tan dulce en nuestra lengua."

# game/episode017.rpy:528
translate spanish ep017_first_dream_bdfc864f:

#   woman "The forbidden love consummated with abandon."
    woman "El amor prohibido consumado con abandono."

