translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_60290687:

#   woman "To what subject does your request pertain?"
    woman "¿A qué asunto se refiere su solicitud?"

# game/episode017.rpy:757
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_3b05d744:

#   zi "I understand we have come at a difficult time, but we would like to learn more about the invasion of your world."
    zi "Comprendo que hemos venido en un momento difícil, pero nos gustaría saber más sobre la invasión de su mundo."

# game/episode017.rpy:759
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_b030a65c:

#   woman "Our planet is turned into a wasteland, what more do you need to know?"
    woman "Nuestro planeta se ha convertido en un páramo, ¿qué más necesitas saber?"

# game/episode017.rpy:762
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_8167ce57:

#   c "We know the Sovereignty is looking for something on your planet, possibly near the capital."
    c "Sabemos que el Soberano está buscando algo en su planeta, posiblemente cerca de la capital."

# game/episode017.rpy:764
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_c8686e0f:

#   woman "And you want to do what, stop them?"
    woman "¿Y qué quieres hacer, detenerlos?"

# game/episode017.rpy:765
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_251ad502:

#   c "We’d like to investigate the situation and possibly stop them."
    c "Nos gustaría investigar la situación y posiblemente detenerlos."

# game/episode017.rpy:766
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_9a22cb66:

#   woman "You’re either delusional or grave robbers."
    woman "O están delirando o son ladrones de tumbas."

# game/episode017.rpy:767
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_d92ce6b7:

#   woman "I have no interest in dealing with either."
    woman "No tengo interés en tratar con ninguno de los dos."

# game/episode017.rpy:769
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_0d556dac:

#   woman "You’re dismissed."
    woman "Puedes retirarte."

# game/episode017.rpy:771
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_491e000a:

#   "Protesting seemed fruitless, so we turned around and left."
    "La protesta parecía infructuosa, así que dimos media vuelta y nos marchamos."

# game/episode017.rpy:773
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_ef68b707:

#   "When we had crossed the residential area, one of the guards hurried towards us."
    "Cuando habíamos cruzado la zona residencial, uno de los guardias se apresuró hacia nosotros."

# game/episode017.rpy:777
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_a9dc289c:

#   woman "I overheard you talking about wanting to get inside the capital."
    woman "Te oí hablar de que querías entrar en la capital."

# game/episode017.rpy:778
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_bfc9bb53:

#   woman "I think I can be of assistance."
    woman "Creo que puedo ser de ayuda."

# game/episode017.rpy:779
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_dd1c5d94:

#   c "Do you have any information?"
    c "¿Tiene alguna información?"

# game/episode017.rpy:781
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_d1683bbc:

#   woman "I do...{w} For the right price..."
    woman "Lo hago...{w} Por el precio correcto..."

# game/episode017.rpy:782
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_fb00336c:

#   c "How much?"
    c "¿Cuánto?"

# game/episode017.rpy:784
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_003e1263:

#   woman "A thousand credits should do the trick."
    woman "Mil créditos deberían bastar."

# game/episode017.rpy:785
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_d07ad229:

#   c "Seven hundred."
    c "Setecientos."

# game/episode017.rpy:786
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_115d305c:

#   woman "Nine."
    woman "Nueve."

# game/episode017.rpy:787
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_d4e17d30:

#   c "Eight."
    c "Ocho."

# game/episode017.rpy:788
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_02871268:

#   woman "Eight fifty, or you can try your luck with the priestess again."
    woman "Ocho cincuenta, o puedes probar suerte con la sacerdotisa otra vez."

# game/episode017.rpy:789
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_8404ab5e:

#   c "Fine."
    c "Bien."

# game/episode017.rpy:791
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_9099e0ac:

#   woman "I want the money upfront."
    woman "Quiero el dinero por adelantado."

# game/episode017.rpy:792
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_8f240135:

#   c "Not going to happen."
    c "No va a suceder."

# game/episode017.rpy:793
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_9a00ed72:

#   c "I can give you a hundred up front."
    c "Puedo darte cien por adelantado."

# game/episode017.rpy:795
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_600d1e78:

#   woman "Half, or no deal."
    woman "La mitad, o no hay trato."

# game/episode017.rpy:796
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_0eeb6918:

#   c "Three hundred and the rest after we receive the info."
    c "Trescientos y el resto cuando recibamos la información."

# game/episode017.rpy:797
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_fa45ed42:

#   woman "Agreed."
    woman "De acuerdo."

# game/episode017.rpy:798
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_65cf6421:

#   "I got out my tablet and wired the amount to the guard."
    "Saqué mi tableta y envié el importe al guardia."

# game/episode017.rpy:799
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_5c44ef4c:

#   c "Your turn."
    c "Tu turno."

# game/episode017.rpy:801
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_b30617c1:

#   woman "Right."
    woman "Bien."

# game/episode017.rpy:802
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_f5e99176:

#   woman "The invading forces are indeed concentrating on the capital."
    woman "Las fuerzas invasoras se están concentrando en la capital."

# game/episode017.rpy:803
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_5b4e37fe:

#   woman "The Grand Arch of Taag is right in the middle of the city and they’re probably trying to reach it."
    woman "El Gran Arco de Taag está justo en el centro de la ciudad y probablemente estén intentando alcanzarlo."

# game/episode017.rpy:804
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_bc50da23:

#   c "What’s so special about that arch?"
    c "¿Qué tiene de especial ese arco?"

# game/episode017.rpy:806
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_da158bb6:

#   woman "It’s one of the major religious buildings on our home world."
    woman "Es uno de los principales edificios religiosos de nuestro mundo."

# game/episode017.rpy:807
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_d131fc9a:

#   woman "Why the Sovereignty has such an interest in the arch, I don’t know."
    woman "Por qué la Soberanía tiene tanto interés en el arco, no lo sé."

# game/episode017.rpy:808
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_5d87092f:

#   woman "The arch has been there for forever, even before the Taagmar ever existed on the planet."
    woman "El arco ha estado ahí desde siempre, incluso antes de que los Taagmar existieran en el planeta."

# game/episode017.rpy:809
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_5c3058d4:

#   c "What makes you think the Sovereignty is targeting the building specifically?"
    c "¿Qué te hace pensar que el Soberano está apuntando al edificio específicamente?"

# game/episode017.rpy:811
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_21fde57b:

#   woman "Multiple strike teams have been intercepted near the arch."
    woman "Múltiples equipos de ataque han sido interceptados cerca del arco."

# game/episode017.rpy:812
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_bfb5a777:

#   woman "Because direct strikes didn’t work out that well for them, they’re just trying to take the whole city and be done with it that way."
    woman "Como los ataques directos no les han funcionado tan bien, intentan tomar toda la ciudad y acabar con ella de esa manera."

# game/episode017.rpy:813
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_dcef3f4f:

#   c "Any other pointers you can give us?"
    c "¿Algún otro consejo que pueda darnos?"

# game/episode017.rpy:815
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_a39928f7:

#   woman "I can give you the exact location of the arch."
    woman "Puedo darle la ubicación exacta del arco."

# game/episode017.rpy:816
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_7a22ad1e:

#   woman "As for landing near the capital, you’re on your own."
    woman "En cuanto a aterrizar cerca de la capital, estás por tu cuenta."

# game/episode017.rpy:818
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_41f41b99:

#   woman "I hope whatever you’re trying to find over there is worth it, as touching down is likely suicide, the entire planet is a warzone."
    woman "Espero que lo que sea que estés tratando de encontrar allí valga la pena, ya que aterrizar es probablemente un suicidio, todo el planeta es una zona de guerra."

# game/episode017.rpy:819
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_b7f4b180:

#   c "Noted."
    c "Tomo nota."

# game/episode017.rpy:820
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_8da22c86:

#   woman "That’s all I know."
    woman "Eso es todo lo que sé."

# game/episode017.rpy:822
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_62f5cc0f:

#   "The guard held her tablet out in response, waiting for the remaining funds to be wired."
    "El guardia le respondió con la tableta en la mano, esperando a que le enviaran los fondos restantes."

# game/episode017.rpy:823
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_2a319f5b:

#   "Begrudgingly, I complied, and then we left without any further pleasantries."
    "Accedí a regañadientes y nos fuimos sin más cumplidos."

# game/episode017.rpy:826
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_af044583:

#   c "A friend of ours is still stuck on your planet and we’re looking for a way to evacuate her."
    c "Una amiga nuestra sigue atrapada en su planeta y buscamos la forma de evacuarla."

# game/episode017.rpy:828
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_ba04762f:

#   woman "Your friend is fighting for the Sovereignty, killing our people?"
    woman "¿Tu amigo está luchando por la Soberanía, matando a nuestra gente?"

# game/episode017.rpy:829
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_bf557386:

#   c "No, not at all."
    c "No, en absoluto."

# game/episode017.rpy:830
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_42c833dc:

#   c "She’s a merchant by trade and happened to be planet-side at the time of the invasion."
    c "Es comerciante y se encontraba en el planeta en el momento de la invasión."

# game/episode017.rpy:831
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_ed6cee27:

#   c "I can assure you that neither we nor she have any love for the Sovereignty."
    c "Le aseguro que ni nosotros ni ella sentimos amor por la Soberanía."

# game/episode017.rpy:833
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_50b2273f:

#   j "Entirely the opposite, I’d venture."
    j "Me atrevería a decir que todo lo contrario."

# game/episode017.rpy:835
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_49827d51:

#   woman "But what knowledge do you seek?"
    woman "Pero, ¿qué conocimientos busca?"

# game/episode017.rpy:836
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_4dceb304:

#   c "From the last message we received from her, she was staying in the planet’s capital."
    c "Por el último mensaje que recibimos de ella, se alojaba en la capital del planeta."

# game/episode017.rpy:837
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_625a84ac:

#   c "The capital supposedly still stands, so we are looking for a way to land somewhere near and extract our friend."
    c "La capital supuestamente sigue en pie, así que buscamos la forma de aterrizar cerca y extraer a nuestro amigo."

# game/episode017.rpy:839
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_fca751fc:

#   woman "That sounds like suicide."
    woman "Eso suena a suicidio."

# game/episode017.rpy:840
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_3ae61e2d:

#   c "She means a lot to us."
    c "Significa mucho para nosotros."

# game/episode017.rpy:842
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_3fb9cc2f:

#   woman "Our latest reports, coming from those who have fled our planet recently, indicate that the planet is surrounded."
    woman "Nuestros últimos informes, procedentes de quienes han huido de nuestro planeta recientemente, indican que el planeta está rodeado."

# game/episode017.rpy:843
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_811b2324:

#   woman "The Sovereignty has so far resisted bombing the city, probably because of the Grand Arch of Taag."
    woman "La Soberanía se ha resistido hasta ahora a bombardear la ciudad, probablemente debido al Gran Arco de Taag."

# game/episode017.rpy:845
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_03b4917e:

#   zi "The Grand Arch?"
    zi "¿El Gran Arco?"

# game/episode017.rpy:846
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_313fabd6:

#   woman "It’s a landmark religious site near the center of the city."
    woman "Es un lugar religioso emblemático cerca del centro de la ciudad."

# game/episode017.rpy:847
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_0862ae4e:

#   woman "The arch was there before us Taagmar sprang into existence on the planet, the capital has grown around it."
    woman "El arco estaba allí antes de que Taagmar surgiera en el planeta, la capital ha crecido a su alrededor."

# game/episode017.rpy:848
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_bf2c051e:

#   woman "The Sovereignty seems to have taken an interest in this structure, considering several strike teams that were intercepted near the building."
    woman "El Soberano parece haberse interesado por esta estructura, teniendo en cuenta varios equipos de ataque que fueron interceptados cerca del edificio."

# game/episode017.rpy:850
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_a574536c:

#   woman "If your friend has been lucky so far, she’ll probably be near the arch, as it’s relatively safe there, currently."
    woman "Si tu amiga ha tenido suerte hasta ahora, probablemente estará cerca del arco, ya que allí es relativamente seguro, actualmente."

# game/episode017.rpy:851
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_74ecb2c9:

#   woman "As for a safe way to enter our planet’s atmosphere, I have no idea, the entire planet is a warzone."
    woman "En cuanto a una forma segura de entrar en la atmósfera de nuestro planeta, no tengo ni idea, todo el planeta es una zona de guerra."

# game/episode017.rpy:852
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_fe7a2df2:

#   c "We understand."
    c "Lo entendemos."

# game/episode017.rpy:853
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_1a66133e:

#   c "We’ll find a way to get to the planet."
    c "Encontraremos la forma de llegar al planeta."

# game/episode017.rpy:854
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_ec51aef4:

#   c "Thank you for the information."
    c "Gracias por la información."

# game/episode017.rpy:856
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_330a548a:

#   "The Taagmar priestess resumed her meditation as we made our way back through the residential area to our ship."
    "La sacerdotisa de Taagmar reanudó su meditación mientras regresábamos a nuestra nave a través de la zona residencial."

# game/episode017.rpy:869
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_c7100d45:

#   c "So, what do you think?"
    c "¿Qué te parece?"

# game/episode017.rpy:872
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_4b92a10c:

#   zi "I’m mostly wondering which friend we’re going to rescue?"
    zi "Me pregunto sobre todo a qué amigo vamos a rescatar."

# game/episode017.rpy:874
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_de695f35:

#   j "I’m mostly wondering which friend we’re going to rescue?"
    j "Me pregunto sobre todo a qué amigo vamos a rescatar."

# game/episode017.rpy:875
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_d6d86f9c:

#   c "I’m sure that will remain a mystery until the heat death of the universe."
    c "Estoy seguro de que seguirá siendo un misterio hasta la muerte por calor del universo."

# game/episode017.rpy:877
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_252e2f3a:

#   zi "Did you really need to lie to the Taagmar priestess?"
    zi "¿Realmente necesitabas mentirle a la sacerdotisa Taagmar?"

# game/episode017.rpy:878
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_0119c04e:

#   c "I didn’t see any other way to give a plausible reason for our interest in the invasion of their capital."
    c "No vi otra forma de dar una razón plausible de nuestro interés en la invasión de su capital."

# game/episode017.rpy:880
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_e6f253be:

#   j "At least we have a clear idea where to look."
    j "Al menos tenemos una idea clara de dónde buscar."

# game/episode017.rpy:882
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_5fd62287:

#   zi "Flying into that warzone with a civilian ship seems incredibly dangerous, though."
    zi "Sin embargo, volar a esa zona de guerra con una nave civil parece increíblemente peligroso."

# game/episode017.rpy:883
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_e85a256a:

#   c "Yes, especially considering the Sovereignty has such a hard-on for us."
    c "Sí, sobre todo teniendo en cuenta que la Soberanía nos tiene manía."

# game/episode017.rpy:884
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_189bb1df:

#   c "They’ll probably flag us the moment we break atmosphere."
    c "Probablemente nos marcarán en cuanto rompamos la atmósfera."

# game/episode017.rpy:886
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_66c09489:

#   j "Maybe Thyia could mask our ship’s identifier again?"
    j "¿Tal vez Thyia podría enmascarar de nuevo el identificador de nuestra nave?"

# game/episode017.rpy:887
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_097b0296:

#   c "Maybe, but that still means landing a non-Sovereignty craft amidst an active conflict."
    c "Tal vez, pero eso sigue significando aterrizar una nave no soberana en medio de un conflicto activo."

# game/episode017.rpy:888
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_18d92ffd:

#   c "I think we need to head back and discuss our options."
    c "Creo que tenemos que volver y discutir nuestras opciones."

# game/episode017.rpy:893
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_6b868edf:

#   "At that moment, we all received an urgent message from Thyia."
    "En ese momento, todos recibimos un mensaje urgente de Thyia."

# game/episode017.rpy:894
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_2c55597d:

#   th "You all need to come back to the Bastard!"
    th "¡Todos tenéis que volver al Bastardo!"

# game/episode017.rpy:895
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_badc6d5b:

#   th "I’ve just spotted Glixken and his mercenaries on the station."
    th "Acabo de ver a Glixken y sus mercenarios en la estación."

# game/episode017.rpy:896
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_058c8683:

#   th "They appear to be looking for us."
    th "Parece que nos están buscando."

# game/episode017.rpy:897
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_0a830946:

#   c "Fuck!"
    c "¡Joder!"

# game/episode017.rpy:898
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_011d031d:

#   c "Let’s run."
    c "Corramos."

# game/episode017.rpy:900
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_e4470065:

#   c "Be careful we don’t run into Glixken on our way to the Bastard."
    c "Ten cuidado de que no nos topemos con Glixken en nuestro camino hacia el Bastardo."

# game/episode017.rpy:902
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_f755e65b:

#   "We reached the docks without encountering Glixken, nor any of his mercenaries."
    "Llegamos a los muelles sin encontrarnos con Glixken, ni con ninguno de sus mercenarios."

# game/episode017.rpy:904
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_f567643a:

#   "Lilly, Thyia and Céline were waiting for us on the bridge."
    "Lilly, Thyia y Céline nos esperaban en el puente."

# game/episode017.rpy:905
translate spanish ep017_docks_refugee_46ea4eab:

#   "The rest of the crew was supposedly spread around the ship to prepare for a hasty departure."
    "Se supone que el resto de la tripulación se repartió por el barco para preparar una salida precipitada."

# game/episode017.rpy:909
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_baf7b638:

#   c "Everyone here?"
    c "¿Están todos?"

# game/episode017.rpy:911
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_113e24a7:

#   l "No, [p_name_short], we're missing Eva."
    l "No, [p_name_short], nos falta Eva."

# game/episode017.rpy:912
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_023d7daa:

#   c "I thought she was with you?"
    c "Creía que estaba contigo."

# game/episode017.rpy:914
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_d94967d7:

#   l "She was, but we got separated when we got the news."
    l "Lo estaba, pero nos separamos cuando recibimos la noticia."

# game/episode017.rpy:915
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_20d5a4b8:

#   l "I looked all over the place for her, but then I had a near run-in with some of Glixken's men."
    l "La busqué por todas partes, pero entonces casi tuve un encontronazo con algunos hombres de Glixken."

# game/episode017.rpy:916
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_aab23d1b:

#   c "Well, fuck!"
    c "¡Bueno, joder!"

# game/episode017.rpy:917
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_d3044c73:

#   c "Isn't she responding to any calls?"
    c "¿No responde a ninguna llamada?"

# game/episode017.rpy:919
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_d380fab3:

#   ce "She isn't, but the coverage isn't great on the lower levels of the station."
    ce "No lo está, pero la cobertura no es muy buena en los niveles inferiores de la estación."

# game/episode017.rpy:921
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_3fe7a298:

#   th "We need to leave, [p_name]."
    th "Tenemos que irnos, [p_name]."

# game/episode017.rpy:923
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_087e56cb:

#   c "And leave my sister here to those fucking mercs?!"
    c "¡¿Y dejar a mi hermana aquí con esos malditos mercenarios?!"

# game/episode017.rpy:925
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_8bc9cafa:

#   c "And leave Eva here to those fucking mercs?!"
    c "¡¿Y dejar a Eva aquí a esos malditos mercenarios?!"

# game/episode017.rpy:926
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_3a8f8e20:

#   c "I'm going to look for her."
    c "Voy a buscarla."

# game/episode017.rpy:928
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_1ccd2c61:

#   l "I’m coming with."
    l "Ya voy."

# game/episode017.rpy:929
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_cb2a96e5:

#   c "No, I can move faster on my own."
    c "No, puedo moverme más rápido por mi cuenta."

# game/episode017.rpy:930
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_b050c436:

#   c "Power up the ship, Céline and wait for me."
    c "Enciende la nave, Céline y espérame."

# game/episode017.rpy:931
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_418db9d9:

#   c "On what level did you leave her behind, Lilly?"
    c "¿En qué nivel la dejaste atrás, Lilly?"

# game/episode017.rpy:933
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_06d67262:

#   l "We were on level six."
    l "Estábamos en el nivel seis."

# game/episode017.rpy:934
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_2dda03fc:

#   c "Good, I'm heading out."
    c "Bien, me voy."

# game/episode017.rpy:935
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_9d63e42b:

#   c "If Glixken and his cronies decide to visit the hangar bay, just fly out of here and put as much distance between you and the station."
    c "Si Glixken y sus compinches deciden visitar la bahía del hangar, simplemente vuela fuera de aquí y pon la mayor distancia posible entre tú y la estación."

# game/episode017.rpy:936
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_69f342b0:

#   c "I'll find some other way to meet up with you all later."
    c "Encontraré otra forma de reunirme con todos vosotros más tarde."

# game/episode017.rpy:938
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_1eed4750:

#   "Before anyone could object, I jumped out of the ship and exited the docks."
    "Antes de que nadie pudiera objetar, salté del barco y salí de los muelles."

# game/episode017.rpy:939
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_4fabba4b:

#   "Level six was on the other side of the station."
    "El nivel seis estaba al otro lado de la estación."

# game/episode017.rpy:941
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_b9a82146:

#   "Luckily, the station was so crowded, I could blend in most of the time."
    "Por suerte, la estación estaba tan abarrotada que pude pasar desapercibido la mayor parte del tiempo."

# game/episode017.rpy:942
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_a28ff3ef:

#   "There was no sight of Glixken or his mercenaries yet."
    "Aún no se veía a Glixken ni a sus mercenarios."

# game/episode017.rpy:943
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_a5e1f494:

#   "As soon as I reached level six, I tried calling Eva again."
    "En cuanto llegué al nivel seis, intenté llamar de nuevo a Eva."

# game/episode017.rpy:944
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_e5db393f:

#   "She still didn’t pick up."
    "Seguía sin contestar."

# game/episode017.rpy:945
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_be24f720:

#   "I was about to put the tablet away when it buzzed."
    "Estaba a punto de guardar la tableta cuando sonó un zumbido."

# game/episode017.rpy:946
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_dee3e53b:

#   "A written message from Eva."
    "Un mensaje escrito de Eva."

# game/episode017.rpy:947
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_d492b027:

#   "“Holed up on level six. Utility room 12B. Glixken mercs everywhere. I don’t know what to do!”"
    "“Atrincherado en el nivel 6. Lavadero 12B. Mercenarios de Glixken por todas partes. ¡No sé qué hacer!”"

# game/episode017.rpy:949
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_a9540014:

#   "I messaged Eva back and told her to sit tight as I started to cross level six to the utility room where my sister was hiding."
    "Le devolví el mensaje a Eva y le dije que se quedara quieta mientras empezaba a cruzar el nivel seis hacia el lavadero donde se escondía mi hermana."

# game/episode017.rpy:951
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_5f9886e8:

#   "I messaged Eva back and told her to sit tight as I started to cross level six to the utility room where my friend was hiding."
    "Le devolví el mensaje a Eva y le dije que no se moviera mientras yo empezaba a cruzar el nivel seis hacia el lavadero donde se escondía mi amigo."

# game/episode017.rpy:952
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_30cec001:

#   "Most of the refugees were concentrated in the areas surrounding the docks, so this level was noticeably less crowded."
    "La mayoría de los refugiados se concentraban en los alrededores de los muelles, por lo que este nivel estaba notablemente menos concurrido."

# game/episode017.rpy:953
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_9fc574b2:

#   "I was about to turn a corner when I heard the grating sound of what I thought was Glixken’s voice."
    "Estaba a punto de doblar una esquina cuando oí el sonido chirriante de lo que me pareció la voz de Glixken."

# game/episode017.rpy:955
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_308edd03:

#   "Looking carefully around the corner, I saw several of Glixken’s mercs patrolling the area."
    "Mirando atentamente a la vuelta de la esquina, vi a varios mercenarios de Glixken patrullando la zona."

# game/episode017.rpy:956
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_5a257408:

#   "Two of them were talking to each other, but Glixken was nowhere in sight."
    "Dos de ellos hablaban entre sí, pero Glixken no estaba a la vista."

# game/episode017.rpy:957
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_29258a06:

#   "The utility room was across the mercs, in a corridor."
    "El lavadero estaba al otro lado de los mercantes, en un pasillo."

# game/episode017.rpy:958
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_550b5f91:

#   "The only way to reach it was to sneak past the patrol."
    "La única forma de llegar a él era escabullirse de la patrulla."

# game/episode017.rpy:959
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_fb4310cf:

#   "Glixken’s men didn’t appear to be on high alert."
    "Los hombres de Glixken no parecían estar en alerta máxima."

# game/episode017.rpy:960
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_28861f26:

#   "While I tried to determine a pattern in their patrols, Glixken arrived."
    "Mientras intentaba determinar un patrón en sus patrullas, llegó Glixken."

# game/episode017.rpy:962
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_4b783539:

#   gl "What the fuck are you still doing here?"
    gl "¿Qué coño haces aquí todavía?"

# game/episode017.rpy:964
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_6c1d4a5a:

#   man "We thought we saw the girl here."
    man "Creímos ver a la chica aquí."

# game/episode017.rpy:966
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_0ae79cb4:

#   gl "And instead of searching, you decided to act like the fucking neighborhood watch?!"
    gl "¡¿Y en vez de buscar, decidiste actuar como el maldito vigilante del vecindario?!"

# game/episode017.rpy:967
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_7369a073:

#   man "We thought-"
    man "Pensamos..."

# game/episode017.rpy:968
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_dc85c132:

#   gl "Shut up and follow me to the docks!"
    gl "¡Cállate y sígueme a los muelles!"

# game/episode017.rpy:969
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_18e70d98:

#   gl "We found their ship, the girl is likely already on it."
    gl "Encontramos su nave, es probable que la chica ya esté en ella."

# game/episode017.rpy:971
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_de80ea84:

#   "I couldn’t hear the rest of what they were saying."
    "No pude oír el resto de lo que decían."

# game/episode017.rpy:972
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_3e488586:

#   "My call to warn Céline of the incoming mercs failed, probably the reason why Lilly lost contact with Eva earlier."
    "Mi llamada para advertir a Céline de la llegada de los mercenarios falló, probablemente la razón por la que Lilly perdió contacto con Eva antes."

# game/episode017.rpy:973
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_fae2ec74:

#   "The crew of the Bastard was on alert, so I just hoped they would escape the docks as soon as Glixken and his troops were spotted."
    "La tripulación del Bastardo estaba en alerta, así que sólo esperaba que escaparan de los muelles en cuanto vieran a Glixken y sus tropas."

# game/episode017.rpy:975
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_fce52292:

#   "My way to Eva was now clear, so I hurried across towards the corridor."
    "Mi camino hacia Eva estaba despejado, así que me apresuré a cruzar hacia el pasillo."

# game/episode017.rpy:976
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_e628bfe6:

#   "The door to room 12B appeared to be locked, so I knocked."
    "La puerta de la habitación 12B parecía estar cerrada, así que llamé."

# game/episode017.rpy:977
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_66b0a42a:

#   c "Eva, it’s me!"
    c "¡Eva, soy yo!"

# game/episode017.rpy:978
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_c1da6d66:

#   "The door slid open in response."
    "La puerta se abrió en respuesta."

# game/episode017.rpy:980
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_43bda2bc:

#   "Eva stood inside the room, holding a wrench and ready to hit me over the head."
    "Eva estaba dentro de la habitación, sujetando una llave inglesa y dispuesta a golpearme en la cabeza."

# game/episode017.rpy:981
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_16e8b20a:

#   e "I’m so glad it’s you."
    e "Me alegro mucho de que seas tú."

# game/episode017.rpy:983
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_c4c59048:

#   e "Are they gone?"
    e "¿Se han ido?"

# game/episode017.rpy:984
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_d96f5eea:

#   c "They are."
    c "Lo son."

# game/episode017.rpy:986
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_9015c3b0:

#   e "I was so scared, [p_name_short]!"
    e "¡Estaba tan asustada, [p_name_short]!"

# game/episode017.rpy:987
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_e5464acb:

#   "Eva trembled as I took her into my arms."
    "Eva temblaba cuando la tomé en mis brazos."

# game/episode017.rpy:988
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_c486755b:

#   e "Lilly and I got separated at some point, and just as I was on my way back to meet her, we got that message from Thyia."
    e "Lilly y yo nos separamos en algún momento, y justo cuando volvía a reunirme con ella, recibimos ese mensaje de Thyia."

# game/episode017.rpy:989
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_84660cfe:

#   e "And then two of those mercenaries came around the corner."
    e "Y entonces dos de esos mercenarios doblaron la esquina."

# game/episode017.rpy:990
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_6e546c65:

#   e "I panicked and ran."
    e "Me entró el pánico y eché a correr."

# game/episode017.rpy:992
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_63d679bd:

#   e "They followed me to this level, but I managed to slip into this room and lock the door."
    e "Me siguieron hasta este nivel, pero conseguí colarme en esta habitación y cerrar la puerta."

# game/episode017.rpy:993
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_557d47fc:

#   e "I don’t think they saw me go in, because they didn’t pursue."
    e "No creo que me vieran entrar, porque no me persiguieron."

# game/episode017.rpy:994
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_66c668ec:

#   e "When I dared to go back out, they were patrolling the area, covering all the exits."
    e "Cuando me atreví a volver a salir, estaban patrullando la zona, cubriendo todas las salidas."

# game/episode017.rpy:995
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_5dd4a361:

#   c "They’re gone now."
    c "Ya se han ido."

# game/episode017.rpy:996
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_d65e25b0:

#   c "Glixken has discovered the ship in the docking bay."
    c "Glixken ha descubierto la nave en el muelle."

# game/episode017.rpy:998
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_ec89e394:

#   e "Oh no!{w} The rest of the crew is aware, right?"
    e "¡Oh, no!{w} El resto de la tripulación es consciente, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode017.rpy:999
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_f3287c7b:

#   c "No, but I told them to keep watch and flee in case of danger."
    c "No, pero les dije que vigilaran y huyeran en caso de peligro."

# game/episode017.rpy:1000
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_161cf5e6:

#   c "I can’t get a message out to the ship from here, but I hope they’re already gone."
    c "No puedo enviar un mensaje a la nave desde aquí, pero espero que ya se hayan ido."

# game/episode017.rpy:1002
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_b83a4818:

#   e "But that means we’re stranded here, doesn’t it?"
    e "Pero eso significa que estamos varados aquí, ¿no?"

# game/episode017.rpy:1003
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_5ea74252:

#   c "Not if I can help it."
    c "No si puedo evitarlo."

# game/episode017.rpy:1004
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_df68c15b:

#   c "Back to the docks."
    c "De vuelta a los muelles."

# game/episode017.rpy:1006
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_c15422a0:

#   "We ran as fast as we could, but skidded to a halt near the first stairway."
    "Corrimos tan rápido como pudimos, pero nos detuvimos cerca de la primera escalera."

# game/episode017.rpy:1008
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_98dba0e3:

#   "Glixken had apparently left a sentry behind who was standing guard at the top."
    "Al parecer, Glixken había dejado atrás a un centinela que montaba guardia en la cima."

# game/episode017.rpy:1010
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_f0d3dde3:

#   "I motioned Eva to hide behind a pillar and drew my gun."
    "Le hice un gesto a Eva para que se escondiera detrás de una columna y desenfundé mi pistola."

# game/episode017.rpy:1014
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_f2dab486:

#   "Luckily, this area of the station wasn't as crowded as the docks, so I didn't think there was much need for stealth."
    "Por suerte, esta zona de la estación no estaba tan abarrotada como los muelles, así que no creí que hiciera falta mucho sigilo."

# game/episode017.rpy:1015
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_6300e757:

#   "The guard didn't have a clue he was about to get shot in the head as I slowly climbed the stairs."
    "El guardia no tenía ni idea de que estaba a punto de recibir un tiro en la cabeza mientras yo subía lentamente las escaleras."

# game/episode017.rpy:1017
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_6094e1d9:

#   "I trained my gun on the back of his head and pulled the trigger."
    "Apunté mi arma a su nuca y apreté el gatillo."

# game/episode017.rpy:1019
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_fef25a91:

#   "The energy beam went straight through his skull, part of it exploding in a spray of blood and gore."
    "El rayo de energía le atravesó el cráneo y parte de él estalló en una salpicadura de sangre y vísceras."

# game/episode017.rpy:1020
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_a7b4c6da:

#   "There was no sound, apart from the fleshy explosion and the last breath gurgling out of the merc's throat as he fell face-first on the floor."
    "No se oyó nada, aparte de la explosión carnosa y el último aliento que brotó de la garganta del mercenario al caer de bruces al suelo."

# game/episode017.rpy:1022
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_853eec1b:

#   "Leaving a dead body out in the open didn't seem like a great idea, so I grabbed his legs and pulled him down the stairs."
    "Dejar un cadáver a la intemperie no me pareció una gran idea, así que le agarré de las piernas y tiré de él escaleras abajo."

# game/episode017.rpy:1023
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_c37f43ed:

#   "The blood smears would undoubtedly be noticed by anyone passing by, but maybe hiding the body would give us some time."
    "Las manchas de sangre sin duda serían notadas por cualquiera que pasara por allí, pero tal vez esconder el cuerpo nos daría algo de tiempo."

# game/episode017.rpy:1025
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_8e63d223:

#   "Together with Eva, I stowed the merc in the storeroom where my sister had hidden herself earlier."
    "Junto con Eva, guardé el merc en el trastero donde mi hermana se había escondido antes."

# game/episode017.rpy:1027
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_2656c57b:

#   "Together with Eva, I stowed the merc in the storeroom where my friend had hidden herself earlier."
    "Junto con Eva, guardé el merc en el trastero donde mi amiga se había escondido antes."

# game/episode017.rpy:1028
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_cf4c19b5:

#   "If Eva was disturbed by my actions, I didn't notice it, she performed the necessary tasks with grim dedication."
    "Si a Eva le molestaban mis acciones, yo no lo notaba, realizaba las tareas necesarias con sombría dedicación."

# game/episode017.rpy:1030
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_c14a04ca:

#   "While this area of the station wasn't as crowded as the docks, people still passed through to get to the residential areas."
    "Aunque esta zona de la estación no estaba tan abarrotada como los muelles, la gente seguía pasando para llegar a las zonas residenciales."

# game/episode017.rpy:1031
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_3f3bede0:

#   "I had to take the merc out quick and silent."
    "Tuve que sacar el mercurio rápido y en silencio."

# game/episode017.rpy:1033
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_ab610ade:

#   "I had my gun trained at the back of his head, just in case, but the guard didn't turn around when I slowly climbed the stairs."
    "Tenía la pistola apuntándole a la nuca, por si acaso, pero el guardia no se volvió cuando subí lentamente las escaleras."

# game/episode017.rpy:1035
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_f3e887b4:

#   "As I neared him, I holstered my weapon and took the merc in a choke hold."
    "Cuando me acerqué a él, enfundé mi arma y cogí al mercenario con una llave de estrangulamiento."

# game/episode017.rpy:1036
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_16791040:

#   "He flailed and tried to wrestle himself away from me."
    "Se agitó y trató de zafarse de mí."

# game/episode017.rpy:1037
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_b8a400cd:

#   "As he was about to cry out, I locked my arm against his windpipe, slowly choking him into unconsciousness."
    "Cuando estaba a punto de gritar, cerré el brazo contra su tráquea, asfixiándolo lentamente hasta dejarlo inconsciente."

# game/episode017.rpy:1038
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_56a7d64f:

#   "When he stopped flailing, I guided the merc towards the floor, kicking away the gun he dropped."
    "Cuando dejó de agitarse, guié al mercenario hacia el suelo, apartando de una patada el arma que había tirado."

# game/episode017.rpy:1040
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_507d472e:

#   "Leaving a body out in the open didn't seem like a great idea, so I grabbed his legs and pulled him down the stairs."
    "Dejar un cuerpo a la intemperie no me pareció una gran idea, así que le agarré de las piernas y tiré de él escaleras abajo."

# game/episode017.rpy:1046
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_5a46fb0f:

#   "Our way clear, we ran towards the docks."
    "Con el camino despejado, corrimos hacia los muelles."

# game/episode017.rpy:1048
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_5d26b1f2:

#   "Nearing the hangar bays, we slowed down, watching for any remnants of Glixken's crew that might still be on the lookout for us."
    "Al acercarnos a los hangares, aminoramos la marcha en busca de restos de la tripulación de Glixken."

# game/episode017.rpy:1053
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_2d1c1b05:

#   "The halls were still filled with refugees, but there was no trace of Glixken or his mercenaries."
    "Los pasillos seguían llenos de refugiados, pero no había rastro de Glixken ni de sus mercenarios."

# game/episode017.rpy:1054
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_db6c7d23:

#   "The Iron Bastard was nowhere to be seen either, its original berth now empty."
    "El Iron Bastard tampoco aparecía por ninguna parte, su atracadero original estaba ahora vacío."

# game/episode017.rpy:1055
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_2a00cbc5:

#   c "I think they've escaped."
    c "Creo que se han escapado."

# game/episode017.rpy:1057
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_ef7539ba:

#   e "What now?"
    e "¿Y ahora qué?"

# game/episode017.rpy:1058
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_8fd9c9f0:

#   c "Now we commandeer a ship."
    c "Ahora comandamos una nave."

# game/episode017.rpy:1060
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_231b8f30:

#   e "Won't station security be all over us?"
    e "¿No estará la seguridad de la estación encima de nosotros?"

# game/episode017.rpy:1061
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_b9de6dcb:

#   c "Only when we fail to secure a ship."
    c "Sólo cuando no conseguimos asegurar un barco."

# game/episode017.rpy:1062
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_3e6d5a86:

#   c "Security is stretched thin as it is because of the refugee crisis."
    c "La seguridad está al límite debido a la crisis de los refugiados."

# game/episode017.rpy:1063
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_4b4f1571:

#   c "I highly doubt they'll be able to get a team to us in time, let alone pursue outside the station."
    c "Dudo mucho que puedan enviarnos un equipo a tiempo, y mucho menos perseguirnos fuera de la estación."

# game/episode017.rpy:1065
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_26172bf6:

#   e "It's risky, but I guess we don't have a choice."
    e "Es arriesgado, pero supongo que no tenemos elección."

# game/episode017.rpy:1066
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_baa4168c:

#   c "I think we don't."
    c "Creo que no."

# game/episode017.rpy:1067
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_153b6e7e:

#   c "Also, I just happen to know which ship to steal."
    c "Además, resulta que sé qué barco robar."

# game/episode017.rpy:1069
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_e42dcaaa:

#   "Eva followed me to the place where I had my encounter with the alien earlier."
    "Eva me siguió hasta el lugar donde antes tuve mi encuentro con el alienígena."

# game/episode017.rpy:1071
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_33ccc2ee:

#   "Their ship was still moored there."
    "Su barco seguía amarrado allí."

# game/episode017.rpy:1072
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_5556fc66:

#   "The canopy was open and the alien was inspecting one of the engines of the vessel."
    "La cubierta estaba abierta y el alienígena inspeccionaba uno de los motores de la nave."

# game/episode017.rpy:1073
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_1e9f3096:

#   c "Stay close."
    c "Quédate cerca."

# game/episode017.rpy:1075
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_1fc2ebb6:

#   "As I approached the alien, I pulled the gun from my holster."
    "Mientras me acercaba al alienígena, saqué la pistola de mi funda."

# game/episode017.rpy:1076
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_bb598f7c:

#   c "Hey, you there!"
    c "¡Eh, tú!"

# game/episode017.rpy:1077
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_83ef93db:

#   c "Remember me?"
    c "¿Te acuerdas de mí?"

# game/episode017.rpy:1078
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_4605924b:

#   "Several bystanders started running at the sight of the unholstered weapon."
    "Varios transeúntes empezaron a correr al ver el arma desenfundada."

# game/episode017.rpy:1079
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_7af0daa7:

#   "I needed to be quick about it, as some of them would undoubtedly alert station security."
    "Tenía que darme prisa, ya que algunos de ellos alertarían sin duda a la seguridad de la estación."

# game/episode017.rpy:1080
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_4721f585:

#   c "Hands in the air."
    c "Manos arriba."

# game/episode017.rpy:1081
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_a6064ca2:

#   c "Slowly step away from your ship."
    c "Aléjese lentamente de su nave."

# game/episode017.rpy:1084
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_9ebfbff3:

#   man "What is it now?"
    man "¿Qué pasa ahora?"

# game/episode017.rpy:1086
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_c9ed515a:

#   man "Haven’t punished me enough?"
    man "¿No me has castigado lo suficiente?"

# game/episode017.rpy:1088
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_6b66297d:

#   man "I apologized, didn’t I?"
    man "Me disculpé, ¿no?"

# game/episode017.rpy:1089
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_4167b6ca:

#   c "I’m in need of a ship."
    c "Necesito un barco."

# game/episode017.rpy:1090
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_59ba0fcc:

#   c "And since you’re a cunt harassing women, I figured I might as well take yours."
    c "Y ya que eres un cabrón acosando mujeres, pensé que también podría tomar la tuya."

# game/episode017.rpy:1091
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_894e9bdb:

#   c "Are the keys still in the ignition?"
    c "¿Están las llaves puestas?"

# game/episode017.rpy:1093
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_c8f7e8fe:

#   man "Fuck you."
    man "Vete a la mierda."

# game/episode017.rpy:1094
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_0101d2e2:

#   c "I take that as a yes."
    c "Lo tomo como un sí."

# game/episode017.rpy:1095
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_97d0dfd9:

#   c "Stay behind me, Eva."
    c "Quédate detrás de mí, Eva."

# game/episode017.rpy:1097
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_015be0df:

#   "The gun still trained on the fuming alien, Eva and I climbed on the wing of the ship."
    "Con el arma aún apuntando al humeante alienígena, Eva y yo subimos al ala de la nave."

# game/episode017.rpy:1099
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_022fdcd8:

#   "The owner was now running towards us, screaming at the top of his lungs."
    "El dueño corría hacia nosotros gritando a todo pulmón."

# game/episode017.rpy:1101
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_b71448e3:

#   "We both strapped in, and I switched on the engines."
    "Nos atamos los dos y encendí los motores."

# game/episode017.rpy:1102
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_32e3afe2:

#   "The canopy of the ship closed, shutting out the angry yells of the alien."
    "La cubierta de la nave se cerró, tapando los gritos furiosos del alienígena."

# game/episode017.rpy:1103
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_896ed572:

#   c "Ready for take-off."
    c "Listos para el despegue."

# game/episode017.rpy:1104
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_cd683b0c:

#   c "Can you see if you can locate the Bastard as soon as we clear the station?"
    c "¿Puedes ver si puedes localizar al Bastardo tan pronto como despejemos la estación?"

# game/episode017.rpy:1105
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_1516c223:

#   e "On it."
    e "En ello."

# game/episode017.rpy:1107
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_3ff945ba:

#   "There were no alarms, nor any communication from the station’s traffic control."
    "No hubo alarmas, ni ninguna comunicación del control de tráfico de la estación."

# game/episode017.rpy:1109
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_ad9e69b7:

#   "Our ship was cleared automatically, and I kicked it into high gear as soon as we sped out of the hangar bay."
    "Nuestra nave fue autorizada automáticamente y yo aceleré a fondo en cuanto salimos del hangar."

# game/episode017.rpy:1110
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_bd6f0ca7:

#   c "Nobody is shooting at us yet."
    c "Nadie nos dispara todavía."

# game/episode017.rpy:1112
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_28372ec1:

#   e "Let’s keep it that way."
    e "Mantengámoslo así."

# game/episode017.rpy:1113
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_0ee159a1:

#   c "Any luck finding the Bastard?"
    c "¿Ha habido suerte encontrando al Bastardo?"

# game/episode017.rpy:1115
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_30a52b9f:

#   e "Not yet..."
    e "Todavía no..."

# game/episode017.rpy:1116
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_8e683b4d:

#   e "I did find a bag of supplies tucked underneath my chair, though."
    e "Sin embargo, encontré una bolsa de provisiones escondida debajo de mi silla."

# game/episode017.rpy:1117
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_30d8bc15:

#   c "Good, at least we’ll have some snacks for this trip."
    c "Bien, al menos tendremos algunos bocadillos para este viaje."

# game/episode017.rpy:1119
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_461c447a:

#   e "Still no sign of the Bastard."
    e "Aún no hay señales del Bastardo."

# game/episode017.rpy:1120
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_a0621e7b:

#   e "Wait!"
    e "¡Espera!"

# game/episode017.rpy:1122
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_afd030ed:

#   e "Yes, they’re still in this system."
    e "Sí, todavía están en este sistema."

# game/episode017.rpy:1123
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_4f0ca6fc:

#   e "Traveling at high speed, though."
    e "Viajando a alta velocidad, sin embargo."

# game/episode017.rpy:1124
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_6af78cfb:

#   c "Then let’s see what this ship can do."
    c "Entonces veamos qué puede hacer esta nave."

# game/episode017.rpy:1125
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_7d409743:

#   c "The owner of this ship being a cunt was just one of the reasons for stealing this particular bucket."
    c "Que el dueño de este barco fuera un cabrón fue sólo una de las razones para robar este cubo en particular."

# game/episode017.rpy:1126
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_ca337bc4:

#   c "This type is often used for races, so it should be able to reach some impressive speeds."
    c "Este tipo se utiliza a menudo en carreras, por lo que debería ser capaz de alcanzar algunas velocidades impresionantes."

# game/episode017.rpy:1128
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_296bd773:

#   e "Enough to overtake the Bastard?"
    e "¿Suficiente para adelantar al Bastardo?"

# game/episode017.rpy:1129
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_6eeb6a30:

#   c "Let’s hope so."
    c "Esperemos que sí."

# game/episode017.rpy:1130
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_a25dfe9e:

#   c "Just be warned, it won’t be a very pleasant flight."
    c "Pero le advertimos que no será un vuelo muy agradable."

# game/episode017.rpy:1132
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_540fef08:

#   e "Understood, just hit it."
    e "Entendido, sólo dale."

# game/episode017.rpy:1134
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_3c69814c:

#   "I accelerated and we stormed towards the coordinates of the Bastard."
    "Aceleré y nos dirigimos hacia las coordenadas del Bastardo."

# game/episode017.rpy:1135
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_a9afa599:

#   "The tremendous forces pressing upon us were almost too much to bear."
    "Las tremendas fuerzas que nos presionaban eran casi demasiado para soportarlas."

# game/episode017.rpy:1136
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_cd43b6c9:

#   "Through clenched teeth, Eva attempted to speak."
    "Con los dientes apretados, Eva intentó hablar."

# game/episode017.rpy:1137
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_0227d02e:

#   e "The...{w} Bastard...{w} Is being...{w} Pursued..."
    e "El...{w} Bastardo...{w} Está siendo...{w} Perseguido..."

# game/episode017.rpy:1139
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_7b9bcf5b:

#   "When we were in range, I hit the brakes, and the pressure eventually returned to normal."
    "Cuando estuvimos a tiro, pisé el freno y la presión acabó volviendo a la normalidad."

# game/episode017.rpy:1140
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_cf578197:

#   "I could see that Eva was right about the Bastard being pursued."
    "Pude ver que Eva tenía razón sobre la persecución del Bastardo."

# game/episode017.rpy:1141
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_db126bdc:

#   c "Probably Glixken trying to catch them."
    c "Probablemente Glixken tratando de atraparlos."

# game/episode017.rpy:1142
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_63923111:

#   e "That seems very likely."
    e "Eso parece muy probable."

# game/episode017.rpy:1143
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_b2abd033:

#   e "They’re flying at approximately the same speed, that other ship trailing some distance behind it."
    e "Están volando aproximadamente a la misma velocidad, la otra nave sigue a cierta distancia detrás de ella."

# game/episode017.rpy:1144
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_f5b93369:

#   c "Let’s see if we can fuck him from behind somehow."
    c "Vamos a ver si podemos cogerlo por detrás de alguna manera."

# game/episode017.rpy:1145
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_52815c57:

#   "Plotting a course to line us up with Glixken and the Bastard, I had Eva unlock the weapons system."
    "Trazando un curso para alinearnos con Glixken y el Bastardo, hice que Eva desbloqueara el sistema de armas."

# game/episode017.rpy:1147
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_bafb3969:

#   "When both ships came into view, our suspicions were confirmed."
    "Cuando ambos barcos aparecieron a la vista, nuestras sospechas se confirmaron."

# game/episode017.rpy:1149
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_188f1b98:

#   "The unknown ship assaulted the Bastard with continuous PBC fire."
    "La nave desconocida asaltó al Bastardo con fuego continuo de PBC."

# game/episode017.rpy:1150
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_be5fc8ed:

#   "They must not have noticed us yet, because both ships remained committed to firing upon each other."
    "No debían de haberse percatado aún de nuestra presencia, porque ambos buques seguían empeñados en dispararse mutuamente."

# game/episode017.rpy:1152
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_17a33c16:

#   c "Ready?"
    c "¿Preparado?"

# game/episode017.rpy:1154
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_e05651bd:

#   e "Ready, on your-"
    e "Listo, en tu..."

# game/episode017.rpy:1156
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_90466b6a:

#   e "Fuck! The Bastard’s been hit."
    e "¡Joder! Le han dado al bastardo."

# game/episode017.rpy:1158
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_9a665faa:

#   "Glixken had indeed scored a direct hit on the Bastard’s rear."
    "Glixken había acertado directamente en la retaguardia del Bastardo."

# game/episode017.rpy:1159
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_0f660a52:

#   "Céline was still trying to evade most of the PBC fire that rained down on them, but they were having an increasingly hard time."
    "Céline seguía intentando esquivar la mayor parte de los disparos de la PBC que llovían sobre ellos, pero cada vez lo tenían más difícil."

# game/episode017.rpy:1160
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_6b9c4871:

#   c "Shoot those fuckers."
    c "Dispara a esos cabrones."

# game/episode017.rpy:1162
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_997fe78a:

#   "Eva loosed our cannons at Glixken."
    "Eva soltó nuestros cañones en Glixken."

# game/episode017.rpy:1164
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_a7077e25:

#   "Possibly due to the fact that we caught them unaware, Eva managed to score a direct hit on Glixken’s ship."
    "Posiblemente debido al hecho de que les pillamos desprevenidos, Eva consiguió asestar un golpe directo a la nave de Glixken."

# game/episode017.rpy:1165
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_f2d883c1:

#   c "Good shot!"
    c "¡Buen tiro!"

# game/episode017.rpy:1167
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_1c69494b:

#   "Our happiness was shortlived, as several of the enemy ship’s cannons turned towards us."
    "Nuestra felicidad duró poco, ya que varios cañones de la nave enemiga se volvieron hacia nosotros."

# game/episode017.rpy:1168
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_2f3137fc:

#   c "Keep firing, I’ll try to evade."
    c "Sigue disparando, intentaré evadirme."

# game/episode017.rpy:1169
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_0e3d1a89:

#   "Glixken now had to divide his attention, allowing the Bastard some respite."
    "Glixken ahora tenía que dividir su atención, permitiendo al Bastardo un respiro."

# game/episode017.rpy:1170
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_b0a5923a:

#   "The distance between the two ships grew, as the Bastard limped away towards a nearby planet."
    "La distancia entre las dos naves crecía, mientras la Bastard se alejaba cojeando hacia un planeta cercano."

# game/episode017.rpy:1171
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_4c2b072a:

#   "Getting out of the firing line proved to be very difficult."
    "Salir de la línea de fuego resultó muy difícil."

# game/episode017.rpy:1172
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_b966ad40:

#   "Glixken must have diverted more power to the cannons trained on us, as our ship shuddered under the barrage of PBC fire."
    "Glixken debe haber desviado más potencia a los cañones apuntándonos, ya que nuestra nave se estremeció bajo el aluvión de fuego de la PBC."

# game/episode017.rpy:1173
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_52689564:

#   c "We can’t sustain much more."
    c "No podemos aguantar mucho más."

# game/episode017.rpy:1175
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_64780330:

#   "Alarms suddenly went off, and the ship indicated we sustained heavy damage on one of the wings."
    "De repente saltaron las alarmas y la nave indicó que habíamos sufrido graves daños en una de las alas."

# game/episode017.rpy:1176
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_e4477a1c:

#   c "I’m going to try and get us out of here."
    c "Voy a intentar sacarnos de aquí."

# game/episode017.rpy:1177
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_04f0ff4d:

#   e "Understood."
    e "Entendido."

# game/episode017.rpy:1179
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_fad91c1b:

#   "Glixken still fired on us as we disengaged and sped towards the same planet the Bastard was heading."
    "Glixken seguía disparándonos mientras nos desacoplábamos y acelerábamos hacia el mismo planeta al que se dirigía el Bastardo."

# game/episode017.rpy:1180
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_2bbe2c9a:

#   "The hit we scored must have seriously hampered their ship, because we easily outpaced them, even with one of our wings in tatters."
    "El impacto que les asestamos debió de afectar seriamente a su nave, porque les superamos fácilmente, incluso con una de nuestras alas destrozada."

# game/episode017.rpy:1182
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_163c1a96:

#   "The planet we were approaching appeared to be a dull red orb."
    "El planeta al que nos acercábamos parecía un orbe rojo opaco."

# game/episode017.rpy:1186
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_3890e7c7:

#   "By now, Glixken was trailing far behind, still firing PBC rounds at regular intervals, but hitting nothing."
    "A estas alturas, Glixken iba muy rezagado, todavía disparando balas PBC a intervalos regulares, pero sin acertar en nada."

# game/episode017.rpy:1187
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_c1d52dad:

#   c "We’re about to break atmosphere."
    c "Estamos a punto de romper la atmósfera."

# game/episode017.rpy:1188
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_9c7e787f:

#   c "Brace yourself."
    c "Prepárate."

# game/episode017.rpy:1189
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_04b3cf92:

#   "Despite the warning, we were both surprised by the roughness of the descent."
    "A pesar de la advertencia, a ambos nos sorprendió la dureza del descenso."

# game/episode017.rpy:1042
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_8e63d223_1:

#   "Together with Eva, I stowed the merc in the storeroom where my sister had hidden herself earlier."
    "Junto con Eva, guardé el merc en el trastero donde mi hermana se había escondido antes."

# game/episode017.rpy:1044
translate spanish ep017_altum_exit_2656c57b_1:

#   "Together with Eva, I stowed the merc in the storeroom where my friend had hidden herself earlier."
    "Junto con Eva, guardé el merc en el trastero donde mi amiga se había escondido antes."

# game/episode017.rpy:1194
translate spanish ep017_crash_6194bd2b:

#   "As soon as we entered the planet’s atmosphere, we were hit by a raging sandstorm."
    "En cuanto entramos en la atmósfera del planeta, nos azotó una furiosa tormenta de arena."

# game/episode017.rpy:1195
translate spanish ep017_crash_df75e619:

#   "The push and pull of the winds was so enormous that I had trouble controlling the ship."
    "El empuje y el tirón de los vientos era tan enorme que me costaba controlar el barco."

# game/episode017.rpy:1196
translate spanish ep017_crash_051bc66d:

#   "Sand got everywhere and the ship’s engine was struggling."
    "Había arena por todas partes y el motor del barco tenía problemas."

# game/episode017.rpy:1197
translate spanish ep017_crash_d120093f:

#   c "I’m going to try and put her down."
    c "Voy a intentar bajarla."

# game/episode017.rpy:1199
translate spanish ep017_crash_7fa5481c:

#   "A great mass of sand approached with rapid speed as I attempted to steer us towards a flat area that would support our landing trajectory."
    "Una gran masa de arena se acercaba a gran velocidad mientras yo intentaba dirigirnos hacia una zona llana que soportara nuestra trayectoria de aterrizaje."

# game/episode017.rpy:1201
translate spanish ep017_crash_447f471c:

#   e "Are we going to make it?"
    e "¿Lo conseguiremos?"

# game/episode017.rpy:1202
translate spanish ep017_crash_91666976:

#   "Considering the turbulence we were experiencing, I couldn’t really reassure her."
    "Teniendo en cuenta las turbulencias que estábamos experimentando, no podía tranquilizarla."

# game/episode017.rpy:1203
translate spanish ep017_crash_0a6af8ef:

#   "The engine wheezed and sputtered as the frame of the ship groaned under the forces that were pulling at us."
    "El motor resollaba y chisporroteaba mientras el armazón de la nave gemía bajo las fuerzas que tiraban de nosotros."

# game/episode017.rpy:1204
translate spanish ep017_crash_6c7af131:

#   e "If we...{w} don’t make it...{w} [p_name_short]..."
    e "Si nosotros...{w} no lo logramos...{w} [p_name_short]..."

# game/episode017.rpy:1205
translate spanish ep017_crash_f45b5675:

#   e "I just want to say that..."
    e "Sólo quiero decir que..."

# game/episode017.rpy:1207
translate spanish ep017_crash_d637dea3:

#   e "I love you."
    e "Te quiero."

# game/episode017.rpy:1209
translate spanish ep017_crash_7fbca8b4:

#   "I didn’t get a chance to reply as the nose of our ship bored into the surface of the planet at that moment."
    "No tuve ocasión de responder, ya que el morro de nuestra nave se clavó en ese momento en la superficie del planeta."

# game/episode017.rpy:1210
translate spanish ep017_crash_77654a3a:

#   "The sea of sand halted our descent abruptly."
    "El mar de arena detuvo bruscamente nuestro descenso."

# game/episode017.rpy:1211
translate spanish ep017_crash_3f6f7a25:

#   "Luckily, we had lost enough speed to avoid getting compressed into paste."
    "Por suerte, habíamos perdido suficiente velocidad para evitar quedar comprimidos en pasta."

# game/episode017.rpy:1212
translate spanish ep017_crash_de98a7cc:

#   "The fire on the wings was now raging, black smoke billowing into the air."
    "El fuego de las alas estaba ardiendo y el humo negro se extendía por el aire."

# game/episode017.rpy:1213
translate spanish ep017_crash_5d172416:

#   "I nearly lost consciousness just before the ship ground to a halt."
    "Casi pierdo el conocimiento justo antes de que la nave se detuviera."

# game/episode017.rpy:1215
translate spanish ep017_crash_64332b2a:

#   "A quick look to my right told me Eva hadn’t been as lucky."
    "Una rápida mirada a mi derecha me dijo que Eva no había tenido tanta suerte."

# game/episode017.rpy:1216
translate spanish ep017_crash_54ef110d:

#   "Quickly, I unfastened the belt securing me in the pilot’s chair and reached over to free Eva."
    "Rápidamente, me desabroché el cinturón que me sujetaba a la silla del piloto y me acerqué para liberar a Eva."

# game/episode017.rpy:1219
translate spanish ep017_crash_02b12b96:

#   "My sister was still out, so I pulled her out of the chair and dragged her body out of the ship."
    "Mi hermana seguía inconsciente, así que la saqué de la silla y arrastré su cuerpo fuera de la nave."

# game/episode017.rpy:1221
translate spanish ep017_crash_19119c9a:

#   "Eva was still out, so I pulled her out of the chair and dragged her body out of the ship."
    "Eva seguía inconsciente, así que la saqué de la silla y arrastré su cuerpo fuera de la nave."

# game/episode017.rpy:1222
translate spanish ep017_crash_fdbe3d84:

#   "The backpack of supplies she’d discovered earlier didn’t seem like a luxury now, so I slung it over my shoulder."
    "La mochila con provisiones que había descubierto antes ya no me parecía un lujo, así que me la colgué del hombro."

# game/episode017.rpy:1223
translate spanish ep017_crash_eb00a34c:

#   "By now, the fire had consumed almost all of the ship."
    "El fuego ya había consumido casi toda la nave."

# game/episode017.rpy:1224
translate spanish ep017_crash_900ef7ea:

#   "I had to get us out of there, because once the fire reached the ship’s fuel tanks, we would be in for a very large explosion."
    "Tenía que sacarnos de allí, porque una vez que el fuego alcanzara los tanques de combustible del barco, nos esperaría una explosión muy grande."

# game/episode017.rpy:1225
translate spanish ep017_crash_01c4e476:

#   "Eva stirred and tried to open her eyes."
    "Eva se revolvió e intentó abrir los ojos."

# game/episode017.rpy:1230
translate spanish ep017_crash_95110dff:

#   "Supporting her, I helped Eva get on her feet, and together we limped away from the wreckage."
    "Apoyándome en ella, ayudé a Eva a ponerse en pie, y juntas nos alejamos cojeando de los escombros."

# game/episode017.rpy:1232
translate spanish ep017_crash_ea19e345:

#   "As we reached the foot of a sand dune, the ship exploded, sending debris high up in the air."
    "Al llegar al pie de una duna de arena, la nave explotó, lanzando escombros por los aires."

# game/episode017.rpy:1233
translate spanish ep017_crash_f32f8db7:

