# game/episode017.rpy:1516
translate spanish ep017_lilly_0fcfb9e9:

#   c "And people would be absolutely scandalized by the fact that a brother and sister had a child."
    c "Y la gente se escandalizaría absolutamente por el hecho de que un hermano y una hermana tuvieran un hijo."

# game/episode017.rpy:1517
translate spanish ep017_lilly_9aea8a21:

#   c "But I just don’t care."
    c "Pero no me importa."

# game/episode017.rpy:1518
translate spanish ep017_lilly_2ab4b3e8:

#   c "I want to share those happy moments with you, Lilly and I hope you feel the same."
    c "Quiero compartir esos momentos felices contigo, Lilly, y espero que tú sientas lo mismo."

# game/episode017.rpy:1520
translate spanish ep017_lilly_07002386:

#   l "I...{w} Yes, of course!"
    l "Yo...{w} ¡Sí, por supuesto!"

# game/episode017.rpy:1521
translate spanish ep017_lilly_5122f40d:

#   l "I must admit I held back a little just now."
    l "Debo admitir que me contuve un poco hace un momento."

# game/episode017.rpy:1523
translate spanish ep017_lilly_c6f4a829:

#   l "I really didn’t lie when I said I was really worried the past few days."
    l "Realmente no mentí cuando dije que estaba muy preocupada los últimos días."

# game/episode017.rpy:1524
translate spanish ep017_lilly_56e14ac3:

#   l "But just the thought of carrying our child filled me with such happiness."
    l "Pero la sola idea de llevar a nuestro hijo me llenaba de felicidad."

# game/episode017.rpy:1526
translate spanish ep017_lilly_f9aa0349:

#   l "Silly daydreams, I know, but still..."
    l "Sueños tontos, lo sé, pero aún así..."

# game/episode017.rpy:1528
translate spanish ep017_lilly_f5cd3e11:

