translate spanish ep017_lilly_7fce3977:

#   l "I know, I came to the same conclusion."
    l "Lo sé, llegué a la misma conclusión."

# game/episode017.rpy:1551
translate spanish ep017_lilly_fbfdd498:

#   l "There was that brief glimmer of desire though, maybe my motherly instincts kicking in."
    l "Sin embargo, hubo un breve atisbo de deseo, tal vez mi instinto maternal se puso en marcha."

# game/episode017.rpy:1553
translate spanish ep017_lilly_0c7e75e0:

#   l "But you’re right, all things considered, being parents isn’t in the cards for us."
    l "Pero tienes razón, considerándolo todo, ser padres no está en nuestras cartas."

# game/episode017.rpy:1554
translate spanish ep017_lilly_c186e211:

#   c "We should maybe be a little more careful from now on."
    c "Deberíamos tener más cuidado a partir de ahora."

# game/episode017.rpy:1556
translate spanish ep017_lilly_607c5088:

#   l "You mean, don’t have sex anymore?"
    l "¿Te refieres a no tener más sexo?"

# game/episode017.rpy:1557
translate spanish ep017_lilly_b022eb1a:

